name: J is for Jamboree!
description:
8 year old Jamboree knows her name means a large celebration or party, typically a lavish and boisterous one, according to the dictionary.  That is why it is perfect for the Rocking New Year JACKPOT event!

Since Jamboree is 8 she does not have a Twitter, but you can contact her art mentor, Lily White, @rblbab with any questions or comments, THANKS!
